MAN FROM U.N.C.L.E. 129 Odd Man Affair

Season closer has Napoleon Solo and Illya Kuryakin forced to work with a former agent to stop &#039;Mr. Zed&#039; from uniting a band of terrorists and forging an alliance with Communist countries.

Stars:Robert Vaughn as Napoleon Solo, David McCallum as Illya Kuryakin, and Leo G. Carroll as Mr. Alexander Waverly
Guest star: Martin Balsam (Albert Sully), Barbara Shelley (Bryn Watson), Ronald Long (Mr. Zed) 

Aired: 19 April 1965
